deck: Created to be a perfect soldier, she took revenge on the murderers of her parents and sister.
description:
Origin

Argent's parents and sister were killed by a secret organization claiming to be the CIA, when a rocket destroyed their yacht. Argent was badly injured, but her ravaged body was molded and trained to be a perfect soldier. But unknown to the organization, Argent's father had, before his death, told Argent about his suspicions of a secret organization. She turned against her trainers and killed them. The angel Yael then asked her to join the Unholy.

Powers & Abilities

Argent has the ability to mentally control her braids. Placed on the end of her braids are sharp knives.

Her DNA is fused with Gorgon DNA. This gives her the power to immobilize a person with a stare, resulting in a total shutdown of the body.
name: Argent

deck: Todd McFarlane is the fictional representation of Todd McFarlane.

Origin

Todd McFarlane is the fictional representation of the author, Todd McFarlane.

Creation

Todd McFarlane was created by Todd McFarlane. He made his first fictional appearance in Spawn Kills Everyone! #1.

Powers and Abilities

Todd McFarlane is the author, he is omnipotent and omniscient in the comic book universe.
